information_extraction_test_request.query: Effectiveness of vertical farming for urban agriculture
information_extraction_test_request.ranking_guidance: Rank papers based on detailed economic and environmental impact analysis.

queries.query: TITLE-ABS-KEY((vertical W/5 farm*) AND (urban W/5 agriculture OR "city farm*") AND (effect* OR efficac* OR benefit* OR performanc*))
TITLE-ABS-KEY(("vertical farming" OR "indoor farming") AND (urban* OR "city*") AND (agriculture OR "food production" OR horticulture) AND (sustainab* OR yield OR output OR economic*))
all:"vertical farming" AND "urban agriculture" AND effectiveness
title:("vertical farming" AND "urban agriculture") AND abstract:("vertical farming" AND "urban agriculture" AND (effectiveness OR efficiency OR benefits OR advantages))

title:("indoor farming" OR "controlled environment agriculture") AND abstract:("indoor farming" OR "controlled environment agriculture") AND ("urban food production" OR "local food systems" OR "city farming") AND (yield OR productivity OR sustainability)
